channel.title: Paying someone to get my server running, easy fix?
channel.description:
Well, I've ran servers in the past on my other computer but the computer that I'm on will NOT work. I always get the error "Port is already open blah blah". I've literally tried everything, had atleast 5 people (experienced RSPS owners) try and help me fix it but a few of them said it's the "Impossible fix error".
I'm willing to pay someone $5 to help me fix this.
Skype: EvilDevilDemented
Cheers.
Here is the error that I am getting: [img]http://puu.sh/3NVrt.png[/img]
